{"id":151627,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/《译者》每日原文推荐-2011510/","date":"2011-05-11T03:30:42Z","modified":"2011-05-11T03:30:42Z","title":"《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/5/10","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【热点新闻</span>/<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">评论】</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2011/may/09/ai-weiwei-arrest-protest-exhibition\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾未未到底在哪里？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（另，</span><span><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2011/may/10/anish-kapoor-ai-weiwei-protest\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">著名雕塑家呼吁为艾未未发起抗议</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-05-10/clinton-asks-china-to-end-deplorable-human-rights-policies.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">希拉里・克林顿要求中国终止</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“令人厌恶”的人权政策</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《电讯报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8505443/China-locks-up-family-of-Mongolian-activist-rights-groups.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人权组织称中国拘捕内蒙活动家的家人</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-05-10/wang-calls-for-shift-in-china-growth-model-as-surplus-jumps.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">王岐山称中国需要改变发展模式</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">商业内幕</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/china-the-low-probability-and-high-impact-worst-case-scenario-2011-5\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国：可能性极低，但影响极大的最坏情况</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国听说</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.chinahearsay.com/xenowhobia-americas-response-to-chinese-investment/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国对中国前来投资的态度：恐华与排外</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律博客</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.chinalawblog.com/2011/05/us_listed_chinese_company_troubles_hidden_in_plain_sight.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在美上市公司的麻烦就在眼皮底下</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/05/09/dear_china_help_us_fix_pakistan\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亲爱的中国，帮我们解决巴基斯坦问题吧</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/11/world/asia/11jasmine.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">茉莉花成敏感词，中国花农遭殃</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110510/wl_nm/us_china_children_sold\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国湖南调查超生儿童被卖给外国人问题</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://globalspin.blogs.time.com/2011/05/09/on-chinas-streets-grisly-attempts-to-cover-up-traffic-accidents/?xid=rss-world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+time%2Fworld+%28TIME%3A+Top+World+Stories%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在中国马路上，为掩盖交通事故不择手段</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（已有</span><span><a href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/200357/193592\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">译文</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/for_american_retailers_chinese_can_be_tough_customers/2011/04/28/AF6VJegG_story.html?wprss=rss_asia-pacific\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对于美国零售商来说，中国顾客难于应付</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/11_20/b4228039775369.htm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新东方帮助中国学生获取美国考试高分</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/bschools/content/may2011/bs2011054_151720.htm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国职业女性对美国</span>MBA<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">趋之若鹜</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/10/business/global/10yuan.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国出口在四月份创下新高</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110510/bs_afp/chinaautosales\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国汽车销量两年来首次下降</span></a></span></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-1485136590373304271?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":263,"categories":[1],"tags":[19306,15522,8840]}